# Tables

## Stack

- Wrap Ant Design Table via `src/component/ui/table.tsx`
- Charts elsewhere: **Recharts** (already used on dashboard)

## Column files

```tsx
// src/columns/organization-table-columns.tsx
import type { ColumnsType } from "antd/es/table";
const ORGANIZATION_TABLE_COLUMNS: ColumnsType<OrganizationRecord> = [ ... ];
export default ORGANIZATION_TABLE_COLUMNS;
```

## Empty state

Pass to `Table`:

```tsx
<Table
  emptyTitle="No organizations found"
  emptyDescription="Get started by creating your first organization."
  emptyAction={<Button type="primary">Create Organization</Button>}
/>
```

## Pagination footer

- Disable built-in table pagination summary defaults when using custom footer
- Use `pagination={false}` on `Table` + manual slice via `paginateItems()` from `helper.ts`
- Render `TablePaginationFooter`: **summary left**, **pagination controls right**
- Page size constants live in data file (e.g. `ORGANIZATIONS_PAGE_SIZE` in `admin-organizations.ts`)

## Toolbar

- Search/filter left; bulk actions right (e.g. Bulk Delete)
- Result count (`Displaying X of Y results`) belongs in **pagination footer**, not the top toolbar
